<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The public method for test() doesn't allow you to set whether to test against the time as the protected method _test() does.</p>

<p>Suggested fix:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
    public function test($id, $doNotTestCacheValidity = false)
    {
        clearstatcache();
        return $this-&gt;_test($id, $doNotTestCacheValidity);
    }
</code></pre>

